Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不后悔？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续留下来会不会更好？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就算继续留在那  也不会有进展的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不喜欢静静等待  暗中观察
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾丝耐心真差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用灿烂的笑容来敷衍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要靠自己的双腿  找到我的师父  maitresse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也不是毫无线索哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父不是在找一样东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  圣者遗物是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有根据  但我觉得到了埃尔塔利亚就会明白些事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是阿尼艾丝的第六感？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界第一人偶师的第六感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:25.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}照れくさいほど近づいて　闻こえたい声がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:25.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}靠近到害羞的距离  为的是听到那个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:32.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ワガママ-ムリ-言いたい放题　闻かせてよアイの正体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:32.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}任性地自说自话  让我领教一下爱的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:40.02,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}むずかしいから逃げちゃった　悲しくて前を见て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:40.02,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}面对困难选择逃避  悲伤地看向前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:47.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}再び发つ大地呼んで　汗握るおおきな满月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:47.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}再次起身召唤大地  满月也捏了一把汗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:54.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}格好イイと格好ワルイ　どうして极端なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:54.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}帅和衰  为什么只有两个极端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:02:04.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大スキで大っキライな事しかわからないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:02:04.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}要不是喜欢就是讨厌  我只知道这两者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:05.67,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}始まった？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:05.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}开始了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:09.06,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LANDS STAR　一种の冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:09.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LANDS STAR  一场冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:12.83,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひとりじゃないって手を系ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:12.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你不是一个人  牵起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:16.14,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}MIGHT STAR　目を闭じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:16.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}MIGHT STAR  闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:20.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わたしともっと息を吸って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:20.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}和我一起接受更多的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:30.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ミライがキレイな方へと动くように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:30.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}愿未来向更美好的方向发展
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:43.23,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,270)\fad(1000,0)}黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:43.23,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,270)\fad(1000,0)}黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:02:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}世界第一的人偶师阿尼艾丝·布兰杰的街上杂技  到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也很精彩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  我正准备去访问Oasis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要委托任务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要登那座山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从前面的矿山发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾丝  走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那奶奶  你认识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉晶石所剩不多了  希望我们去取一些回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她经常来看阿尼艾丝的杂技呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说是一位特别的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是阿尼艾丝的超级铁杆FANS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级铁杆FANS…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她对我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树叶间隙照进来的阳光真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的风景  风格和水之都埃尔塔利亚正相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔兔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳  跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但清澈又好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像大家一起来郊游了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郊游啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是这次的任务比较轻松  才会让人有这样的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  万一出来个晶石怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来收拾就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时就拜托你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着温泉晶石  出发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉晶石啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定准备集体泡温泉HAPPY一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和雷斯塔混浴？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  混浴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混浴啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得追上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始绕前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要追上  莉特丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  前方是悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我说晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林充满了危险呢  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好破旧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封闭的矿山嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么挖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先随便看准一个地方挖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  差不多这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着冒出类似白粉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感受到微弱的艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是温泉晶石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西会在热水中慢慢融化  使艾尔充斥其中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这块算非常小的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先在这里吃一顿中饭  大家看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶  开饭开饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饱了饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的阿尼艾丝比平时更加努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是特别的客人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你也说过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那奶奶是我来到埃尔塔利亚遇到的第一位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后经常来看我的杂技
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉只要有那位奶奶给我鼓掌  我就能精神百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才那么有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据地图  应该是走这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:11.62,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}みんなで　今日は　流れ星　数えようよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:11.62,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}今天  大家一起  数流星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:17.18,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}远足みたい　お果子とか持ってこ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:17.18,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}像郊游一样  带着点心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:23.81,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ふるえるココロに　ちゃんと气がついてくれてた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:23.81,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我颤抖的心  你注意到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:29.58,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}优しいあなたと　强くなれるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:29.58,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}和温柔的你在一起  我能变得更坚强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西是上等货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  开始采集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.78,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}さあ　ノッキンノッキン　たたいちゃえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.78,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}来吧  咚咚  咚咚  敲起门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.37,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}扉はどっちにひらくかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.37,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}门会向哪个方向开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:41.67,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}冒险だいすき　あたらしい出会い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:41.67,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}最喜欢冒险  新的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  虽然封得很好  但有挖过的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:44.75,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あれ？　ドキドキ　どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:44.75,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}奇怪  心跳得好快  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:48.48,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ほほえむことが　乐しいんでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:48.48,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}微笑是那么的愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然藏得这么隐蔽  好期待里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:52.90,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}まいにち笑颜がいちばん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:52.90,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}每天都微笑  才是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面有什么气息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:57.23,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}梦よ、ひらけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:57.23,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}愿梦想  在此刻开启
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉轻飘飘的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活力不断涌现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那继续说刚才的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始以为是遇难者发出的SOS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有人怀疑是恶作剧  不过似乎并非这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是谁出于什么目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之是道不可思议的谜之光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谜之光？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从前面的矿山发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三  二  一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉看着那个  精神就会变好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这东西究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道这是什么  不过是危险物的可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙缇知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况说明  可感受到复杂的流向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复杂的流向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断层出现偏差  具现化  确认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  姐姐  在秀性感镜头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是  快救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然想趁此提升人气  真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地…地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震级不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  阿尼艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:11:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米内特  危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事  大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜  米内特  切露西  尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探戈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边人都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾丝  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探戈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许只能先顺着我们过来的路出去  然后求助了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是…  雷斯塔  还有阿尼被关在了里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能丢下他们  要是再地震的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜  我们也会自己寻找出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是雷斯塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得振作  卡莉娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静  我和雷斯塔没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还有下一波地震
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不能迅速会合  那各自寻找出口才是最佳选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来比一比  是爸爸你们先出去  还是我们先出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米内特  我们也不会输的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一会见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探戈  大家就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏有阿尼艾丝在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里  你这样夸我也没好处的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说真伤脑筋了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得尽快了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  阿尼艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾丝  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的风景  我之前也看过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是像今天一样  出不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拚命寻找出口  最后终于到了外面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候天空也是像这样挂着彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜意识里  觉得就算被雷斯塔看穿了也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔知道我其实是害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想  到了紧要关头就算抱着雷斯塔哭也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没看出你是这样想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能依靠的人在我身边  反倒能让我更加勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  谢谢你  雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  得找大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  阿尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  大家都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此提一个问题  我们去了哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐来回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郊游
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得今天这么聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可能  有事  非常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  阿尼艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我想到一块去了  当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是温泉晶石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采集到了很多  所以分你们点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的好心感动死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:18:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  这是雷斯塔暗示想和我一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  洗澡间空着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让卡莉娜她们先洗比较合适吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个洗对女人的皮肤不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶很高兴  真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉阿姨让我先洗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是妈妈的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摆了一道  那个调皮的性恶作剧者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶  温泉哦  温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待温泉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  阿尼不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶  她去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我似乎察觉到了气息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿别被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  心跳得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  泡温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像不用藏起来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说的确…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.57,0:20:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到被雷斯塔看光光后  还要贴在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很害羞  不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼  你去哪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺激吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  刚才的气息是阿尼艾丝发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想偷偷欣赏大家的裸体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也用不着偷偷看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气  细细品味你们三个的裸身了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要品味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可以  阿尼  米内特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的胸不大  其实没什么好看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切露西好光滑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  不愧是卡莉娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  阿尼  别…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑溜溜  好光滑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软乎乎的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:09.02,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}身近にいてもよく知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:09.02,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即便在身边  也不是什么都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:16.60,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ため息　心配を乘せて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:16.60,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叹息中蕴含着心里的担心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:24.55,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この街を拔ける　明日を想う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:24.55,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心想着离开这座城市的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:27.46,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なにか言ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:27.46,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}真心希望你能说些话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:31.24,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なにか…おねがい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:31.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}真心希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:38.47,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}“梦を见たけど忆えてないの”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:38.47,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}“虽然做了一个梦  但却不记得了”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:45.03,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたふりが下手だと教えないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:45.03,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}请别和我说  我不擅长假装忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:51.50,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まっすぐなキモチが前を见てる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:51.50,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}率直的感情面向着前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:54.83,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喜びを见てる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:54.83,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}面向着喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:00.24,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}迷い消して　Ride on  Ride on RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:00.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}消除心中的迷茫  Ride on  Ride on RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:05.79,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まっすぐに风がえがく回扫线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:05.79,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}率直的风描绘着回归线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:07.76,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}气がついたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:07.76,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一旦注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:19.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah  ときめき眠る前に早く…早く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:19.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在心动不已的感觉消失前  赶紧行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  你怎么自己跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  得赶紧告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oasis工会今天放假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然形势大变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我接受的委托  我要自己完成
